title: can't checkout with svn after r37739?
body:
```bash
svn co https://github.com/golang/go/trunk golang/go
svn: E175002: 意外 HTTP 状态 504 “Gateway Timeout”于“/golang/go/!svn/vcc/default”

svn: E175002: 额外错误:
svn: E175002: REPORT 请求于 '/golang/go/!svn/vcc/default' 失败: 504 Gateway Timeout
```

other repo works fine.
